Fukrey is an upcoming Hindi comedy film directed by Mrighdeep Singh Lamba of Teen Thay Bhai fame starring Pulkit Samrat, Manjot Singh, Ali Fazal, Richa Chadda, Vishakha Singh and Priya Anand in the lead roles.The story and dialogues are written by Vipul Vig and the screenplay was written by Vipul Vig and Mrighdeep Singh Lamba.
